msgid "Gahahh..."
msgstr "Gahahh..."

#: Sceptre_of_Fire/scenarios/deaths.cfg:22
msgid "Maghah..."
msgstr "Maghah..."

#: Sceptre_of_Fire/scenarios/deaths.cfg:35
msgid "Alnnn..."
msgstr "Alnnn..."

#: Sceptre_of_Fire/scenarios/deaths.cfg:48
msgid "Gaanngh..."
msgstr "Gaanngh..."

#: Sceptre_of_Fire/scenarios/deaths.cfg:61
msgid "Kraa..."
msgstr "Kraa..."

#: Sceptre_of_Fire/scenarios/deaths.cfg:74
msgid "Ayahahh..."
msgstr "Ayahahh..."

#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Caravan.cfg:4
msgid "Empty Caravan"
msgstr "Leerer Wagen"

#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Caravan.cfg:14
msgid ""
"Caravans are used to carry gold or supplies over long distances. This one is "
"waiting to be stocked."
msgstr ""
"Wagen werden benutzt, um Gold oder andere Güter über lange Stecken zu "
"transportieren. Dieser wartet darauf, beladen zu werden."

#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Caravan.cfg:17 Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Caravan.cfg:42
msgid "none"
msgstr "keine"

#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Runemaster.cfg:33
#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Smith.cfg:26
#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Runesmith.cfg:32
#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Caravan.cfg:18 Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Caravan.cfg:43
#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Arcanister.cfg:30
msgid "impact"
msgstr "Wucht"

#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Caravan.cfg:28
msgid "Loaded Caravan"
msgstr "Beladener Wagen"

#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Caravan.cfg:39
msgid ""
"Caravans are used to carry gold or supplies long distances. This caravan is "
"already carrying cargo. Because of the immense weight of the cargo, it moves "
"very slowly."
msgstr ""
"Wagen werden benutzt, um Gold oder andere Güter über lange Stecken zu "
"transportieren. Dieser Wagen ist bereits beladen. Aufgrund des imensen "
"Gewichtes der Ladung bewegt er sich nur sehr langsam voran."

#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Arcanister.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Arcanister"
msgstr "Runengroßmeister"

#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Arcanister.cfg:25
msgid ""
"The most powerful of all the runecrafters, the Dwarvish Arcanister destroys "
"wounded enemies almost instantly, and rarely fails to cause a wound when "
"that is his intent. His skill in runecrafting is unrivaled, and the glyphs "
"he carves into his weapons and armor deflect the blows of his enemies."
msgstr ""
"Die mächtigsten aller Runenschmiede, die Runengroßmeister, zerschmettern "
"ihre Gegner beinahe direkt und verfehlen einen Gegner nur äußerst selten. "
"Seine Fähigkeiten im erschaffen von Runen ist uneinholbar und die Glyphen in "
"seinen Waffen und seiner Rüstung wehren die Angriffe seiner Gegner ab."

#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Runemaster.cfg:32
#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Smith.cfg:25
#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Runesmith.cfg:31
#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Arcanister.cfg:29
msgid "hammer"
msgstr "Hammer"

#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Runemaster.cfg:34
#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Arcanister.cfg:31
msgid "magical"
msgstr "magisch"

#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Miner.cfg:4
#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Miner.cfg:38
#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Miner.cfg:72
msgid "Dwarvish Miner"
msgstr "Zwergen Bergmann"

#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Miner.cfg:14
msgid ""
"Dwarvish miners are the grunt workers of Dwarvish society. They take the "
"precious ores out of the ground, but do not ever take part in the crafting "
"of weapons or artifacts."
msgstr ""
"Zwergen Bergmänner sind die Knechte des Volkes der Zwerge. Sie holen die "
"Kostbarkeiten aus dem Gestein, schmieden allerdings nie Waffen oder "
"Artefakte."

#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Miner.cfg:17
#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Miner.cfg:51
#: Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Miner.cfg:85
